item.dc:creator: @Aces316rocks Aces316rocks
item.description:
@Aces316rocks wrote:

Did you make sure you point-forwarded your local and public ip?
Open the start menu and click run. Type in cmd
A comamnd prompt will open. Type ipconfig and the copy IP address for your point forwarding. Use the proper port that others will have to use to connect to you.
